latestPosts.caption:
What started as “just for fun” slowly became our thing.
We didn’t expect the sleepless nights, the long shoots, the constant balancing act between content and our interior business.
But none of it ever felt like a burden because we truly loved doing it❤️

This journey brought us closer, pushed us harder, and gave us something we now call home🥺
And it only means something because you guys were here for it.

Thank you for cheering us on.
For every like, message, and smile you sent our way.
This is as much yours as it is ours❤️
-
The TaRo Tales

latestPosts.caption:
I can’t believe I’m standing here, witnessing the awe-inspiring Sagrada Familia. Knowing that this masterpiece has been under construction since 1882 makes it even more surreal. Antoni Gaudí’s vision is unlike anything I’ve ever seen—every curve, every detail feels like a divine story frozen in time. It’s a moment I’ll never forget❤️
.
